item.title: I have an ip and a scape download now what?
item.dc:creator: @I_Br3ndan_I I Br3ndan I
item.description:
@I_Br3ndan_I wrote:

Double-click you’re compiler/runserver.bat and run you’re server. Then log in via MoparScape WebClient/Client using you’re No-IP domain and whatever password and username.

Note : You need to have you’re No-IP DUC open and running
